07:06.519 --> 07:14.667
Thank God for this odd habit of mine that I think through every draft rather than rewrite.

07:14.687 --> 07:15.348
And write them down.

07:15.648 --> 07:16.669
I do the same thing.

07:16.689 --> 07:17.690
Really, really?

07:17.770 --> 07:19.432
Yeah, I don't have an outline.

07:19.452 --> 07:22.615
My book was 638 pages.

07:22.780 --> 07:23.561
papers together.

07:23.581 --> 07:24.321
There's no papers.

